isthmus to join the atlantic and pacific oceans their mission 
mandated by the 1977 panama canal treaties is twofold to protect 
the waterway but to prepare to turn that job over to the 
panamanians on dec 31 1999 a socalled neutrality treaty 
however provides an openended american military presence to 
guarantee the permanent neutrality and operation of the canal 
alleged election fraud by panamas de facto ruler gen manuel 
