conflict of interest in bradley receiving payment to serve on the 
boards of the two financial institutions while they did business 
with the city 
in addition the securities and exchange commission is looking 
into stock investments handled for bradley by drexel burnham 
lambert 
i was insensitive not to realize that accepting outside 
