did national security adviser robert mcfarlane know about mr 
rodriguezs mission prosecutor john keker asked north 
yes i believe he did north testified in fact i believe 
that once i had talked to mr gregg about it i talked to mr 
mcfarlane about it about the fact that he would be able to assist 
in that country 
gregg testified in a sworn deposition to the congressional 
