amin gemayel expired in september and parliament could not agree on 
a successor gemayel appointed aoun the army commander and 
moslems swore allegiance to hoss the incumbent premier 
by unwritten agreement since independence from france in 1943 
the president is christian the premier sunni moslem and the 
parliament speaker shiite moslem 
