to 3 cents lower with may at 276 a bushel oats were 1 cents 
lower to cent higher with may at 184 a bushel soybeans were 
6 cents to 10 cents lower with may at 751 a bushel 
the rise in oil prices spurred a moderate advance in 
preciousmetal prices which tend to increase with signs of higher 
inflation 
